      "body": "I don't think this patch solves a clear problem that is worth the review cycles for this project and I'm also not sure if this patch is actually correct. The motivation for the change seems weak to me, we have many other places where a bad_alloc exception would lead to an inconsistent state. Since review cycles are the scarcest resource of this project, I'm going to close this PR again.",
